[FILE:417:descriptions/desc.primary]
iocell is a zero dependency drop in jail/container manager amalgamating
some of the best features and technologies FreeBSD operating system has
to offer.  (This package is exclusively for FreeBSD!)

It is geared for ease of use with a simple and easy to understand
command syntax.

iocell has been forked from iocage with the goal of keeping original
iocage experience available, providing bugfixes and new features.


